n    事務官提出異議。\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　111 　年　　10　　月　　5 　　日\r\n                          司法事務官　郭伊恩","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/PTDV/111%2c%e5%8f%b8%e8%81%b2%2c119%2c20221005%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"PTDV,111,司聲,119,20221005,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"司聲","JNO":"119","JDATE":"20221005","JTITLE":"確定訴訟費用額"}